      "parameters": {
        "width": 672,
        "height": 944,
        "content": "\n# üöÄ Automated Plagiarism Checker Workflow in n8n\n\n## ‚úÖ **Short Summary**\n\nAn automated plagiarism detection workflow using n8n, Google Sheets, and a third-party API. It checks submitted text for plagiarism, sends a formatted report via email, and logs results in real-time.\n\n---\n\n## üíº **Use Case**\n\n* Ideal for educators, content teams, academic institutions, or editors who need to verify originality of text submitted via a Google Sheet form.\n\n\n## üéØ **Key Benefits**\n\n* üîÅ **Fully Automated**: No manual checking ‚Äî it triggers on new Google Sheet entries.\n* üì© **Instant Reports**: Sends clean, detailed HTML reports directly to the user's inbox.\n* üìä **Status Tracking**: Logs success or failure directly in your Google Sheet.\n* üö® **IT Alerts**: Notifies your IT team if API or checks fail.\n\n\n"
